    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Before you start cooking, take your <strong>chicken</strong> out of the fridge, open the packet and let it air, then boil a kettle</p><p>Chop your <strong>sweet potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Chop your<strong> potato[es]</strong> (skins on) into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Trim your <strong>green beans</strong></p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-chicken-breast-sweet-potato-mash-and-beans/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> chopped potatoes </strong>and<strong> sweet potatoes</strong> to a pot with a lid with plenty of <strong>boiled water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to medium-high and cook for an initial 6-8 min</p><p>Reboil half a kettle</p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-chicken-breast-sweet-potato-mash-and-beans/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your<strong> chicken </strong>to a clean chopping board</p><p>Cover with <strong>cling film</strong> and bash with a <strong>rolling pin</strong> until flattened to approx. 1cm thickness</p><p>Add your <strong>southern fried seasoning</strong> and <strong>ground smoked paprika</strong> to a plate with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Press the <strong>flattened chicken </strong>onto the plate to evenly coat all over \u2013 this is your <strong>coated chicken</strong></p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-chicken-breast-sweet-potato-mash-and-beans/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated chicken</strong> to the pan and cook for 5-6 min on each side or until browned and cooked through (no pink meat!) \u2013 this is your <strong>southern-style chicken</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 5? Use two pans!</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-chicken-breast-sweet-potato-mash-and-beans/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>After the potatoes have had an initial 6-8 min, add the <strong>trimmed beans</strong> to a <strong>sieve </strong>and set it over the pot</p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for a final 7-8 min, or until the green beans are tender with a bite and the potatoes are fork-tender</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-chicken-breast-sweet-potato-mash-and-beans/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Whilst the potatoes and beans are cooking, chop your<strong> chives </strong>finely</p><p>Combine your<strong> gravy base </strong>with 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>and whisk thoroughly until completely combined \u2013 this is your <strong>gravy mix</strong></p><p>When everything is almost ready, put the <strong>gravy mix</strong> in the<strong> microwave</strong> for 1 min on high or until thickened and stir it all together \u2013 this is your<strong> gravy</strong></p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-chicken-breast-sweet-potato-mash-and-beans/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the potatoes are fork tender, set aside the <strong>green</strong> <strong>beans</strong> and drain the <strong>potatoes</strong></p><p>Return the <strong>drained potatoes </strong>to the pot with a splash of<strong> milk</strong>, a small knob of <strong>butter</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mash the potatoes roughly, then stir through the <strong>chopped chives</strong> \u2013 this is your <strong>chive sweet potato mash</strong></p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/southern-style-chicken-breast-sweet-potato-mash-and-beans/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> southern-style chicken</strong> over the <strong>chive sweet potato mash</strong> with the <strong>green beans </strong>to the side</p><p>Pour the <strong>gravy</strong> all over</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
